onlyOnePlayer: Only one player can be used as argument
ownerTransferFail: Only the owner may transfer claims
ownerTransferNoBlocks: The new owner doesnt have enough claimblocks
ownerTransferNoBlocksAdmin: You can ignore this by switching to admin mode
noPermission: You don't have the required permissions to do that here!
noPermissionSimple: Sorry you can't do that here!
minClaimSize: This is too small. Minimum claimsize is %d
landClaimDisabledWorld: Claiming is disabled in this world
wrongMode: Wrong claim mode. You are in %s-mode
stringScreenReturn: Click on paper to go back
playerModify: Modified permission group for following players to %1$s: %2$s
playerModifyNo: Couldn't set permission group for the players. Probably cause they already belong to a group
playerGroupAddFail: Couldn't add that player to the group either cause the player is already in a group or no player matching the name was found
deleteAllClaimConfirm: Are you sure you want to delete all claims? Type it again to confirm
deleteClaimError: You can't delete this claim here
deleteSubClaimAll: All Subclaims from this claim deleted
editPersonalGroup: Default permission %1$s for group %2$s now set to %3$s
adminDeleteAll: Deleted all claims for following players: %s
readConflict: %1$s conflicts with existing claims. Not added to world! Conflicts:
trappedFail: Rescue not necessary or already rescuing
unlockDropsCmd: Your deathitems are protected. Use %s to unlock them for other players
unlockDrops: Your deathitems are now unlocked for %s ticks
claimNameUsed: The owner of the claim already has another claim with the same name
claimNameUsedSub: One of the subclaim of this claim already has this name
teleportHome: Teleporting to claim home. Don't move for 5 seconds
EDITCLAIM.desc: Gives permission to edit (resize, delete...) the claim
EDITPERMS.desc: Gives permission to change the claims permissions
EDITPOTIONS.desc: Gives permission to edit the claims potion effect
BREAK.desc: Permission to break blocks in the claim
PLACE.desc: Permission to place blocks in the claim
OPENCONTAINER.desc: Permission to open containers (chest, furnace etc.)
BUTTONLEVER.desc: Permission to trigger levers and buttons
ITEMFRAMEROTATE.desc: Permission to rotate items in item frames
LECTERNTAKE.desc: Permission to change books in a lectern
PROJECTILES.desc: Permission to let shot projectiles interact with blocks (e.g. arrow on button)
TRAMPLE.desc: Permission to enable block trampling (farmland, turtle eggs)
RAID.desc: Permission to trigger raids in claim. Wont prevent raids (just) outside
BUCKET.desc: Permission to take liquids with buckets
ANIMALINTERACT.desc: Permission to interact with animals (e.g. shearing sheeps)
XP.desc: Permission to pick up xp orbs
ARMORSTAND.desc: Permission to interact with armor stands
BREAKNONLIVING.desc: Permission to break things like minecarts or armor stands
CANSTAY.desc: Allow player to enter your claim
TELEPORT.desc: Allow player to teleport to your claim home position
WITHER.desc: Toggle wither breaking blocks in claim
ENDERMAN.desc: Allow enderman picking and placing blocks
PISTONBORDER.desc: Toggle piston pull/push across claim borders

teleport: Teleport to the given claims home position. Use admin to teleport to admin claims
claimInfo: Prints infos about the claim you're standing in.
readGriefPrevention: Parses data from the GriefPrevention plugin to Flan.
deleteAllSubClaims: Deletes all subclaim of the current claim.
addClaim: Creates a claim with the given positions. Same as using the claim tool.
personalGroups: Opens the gui to edit personal groups.
adminDelete: Force deletes the current claim or deletes all claims from the specified player.
adminMode: Switches to admin mode ignoring all claims.
sellBlocks: Sells <amount> claimblocks. Needs gunpowder currency installed.
group: - Adds/removes the group with that name. Also editable via the claim menu.
- Adds/remove a player to the group. If overwrite then will overwrite the players current group else does nothing. Also editable via the claim menu.
buyBlocks: Buys <amount> claimblocks. Needs gunpowder currency installed.
trapped: If in a claim not owned by the player attempts to teleport the player out of it after 5 seconds.
deleteAll: Deletes all your claims (you need to double type to confirm it so no accidents).
unlockDrops: Unlocks dropped items from death so other players can pick them up too. Or all of the given players (needs OP)
permission: Sets global/group/personal permissions. Also editable via the claim menu (for group perm right click on the group in the menu).
setHome: Standing in a claim with sufficient permission sets that claims home to the players position
menu: When standing in a claim you have permissions for opens the claim menu.
list: Lists all claims you have. If op also gives ability to list other players claims.
listAdminClaims: Lists all admin claims in the current world.
help: Shows all available commands or info for the given command.
setAdminClaim: Sets a claim to an admin claim.
transferClaim: Gives ownership of the claim to the specified player. Only works if you're the claim owner.
giveClaimBlocks: Gives a player additional claim blocks.
name: name self <name>
Sets the current claims name
switchMode: Switch between normal and subclaim mode.
